<DOC><DOCNO> AP880922-0071 </DOCNO><FILEID>AP-NR-09-22-88 0935EDT</FILEID><FIRST>r w PM-ScissorRecall 1stLd-Writethru a0520 09-22 0128</FIRST><SECOND>PM-Scissor Recall, 1st Ld-Writethru, a0520,120</SECOND><HEAD>K mart Recalls Scissors Desk Sets</HEAD><NOTE>Eds: CORRECTS K Mart to K mart throughout.</NOTE><DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE><TEXT>   Some 48,000 scissors desk sets that could posea hazard to children are being recalled by K mart Corp., theConsumer Product Safety Commission announced today.   The ``School Days Scissors Desk Set,'' includes a razor bladecutting knife that could pose a danger to children, the agencysaid. The set sold for less than $1 in K mart stores during Julyand included the scissors, pencil sharpener and the cutting knife.   Parents should remove the set from use by children and return itto the nearest K mart for a refund, the commission said.   Persons needing more information can contact the commission at1-800-638-2772.</TEXT></DOC>